{"tid":329394,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[青樓雅士]直播Saigon淫賤ocamp","createTime":"2017-07-20T10:34:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-04T07:21:16.000Z","uid":51348,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ae5a850c5560595366ddc32e453e4b766b9cd5aa","tid":329394,"uid":51348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:34:54.000Z","msg":"讀大學時ocamp就玩過唔少，但每次都覺得差咁d嘢，唔夠盡興。畢業之後做左幾年嘢，一路都心有不甘，keep住諗可以點改革ocamp文化。呢個pre camp季節，我決定用行動話俾大家聽，一個最盡興既ocamp應該係點既。營地喺西貢，不過係越南嗰個！<br />\n<br />\n各oc ,組爸可以參考下。<br />\n<br />\n今日一落機放低行李，即刻衝左去食生牛河，一來醫肚，二來壯陽<img src=\"https://holland.pk/lxfj2owk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flxfj2owk&h=446fc211&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/hemvl12j\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fhemvl12j&h=e2664a43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食完已經四點幾 西貢呢邊夜生活好早開始，六點就要開始揀女，食頭啖湯。好在呢間食店喺k場附近，食完仲可以飲杯啡，開post等唱k<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/yn3qt0dc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fyn3qt0dc&h=909d4daf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ddd25e9cddd4d9242cd8b761ebbd3310fc9b6349","tid":329394,"uid":36423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:38:11.000Z","msg":"去11區?"},{"pid":"e980d1d4334822abbe3d8ba7346a00df5526b58f","tid":329394,"uid":51348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:39:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去11區?</blockquote><br />\n太撚遠，依家喺七區"},{"pid":"465c36205f3ec4890e8b0ee68b15280caae6e7d1","tid":329394,"uid":65612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:42:20.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"d11651f1276541f7590e4613a54961d97ed74bef","tid":329394,"uid":51348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T11:07:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ilsnw75r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Filsnw75r&h=80ac857d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌係咁落雨，好撚煩<br />\n呢間係全越南最撚貴既k場，聽聞好多女都識講普通話<br />\n組女就喺呢度搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地企左喺門口，好撚多女返工<br />\nscreen緊"},{"pid":"991c70e19c205da875f6d6f3643505c9f50da47d","tid":329394,"uid":51348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T11:18:06.000Z","msg":"太多正女，起碼要坐兩個"},{"pid":"25191fda3ed4dfedb278a25bd7064cc436f361b9","tid":329394,"uid":8674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T11:24:39.000Z","msg":"Fortune 好似七點先齊女架wor"},{"pid":"0e62b0c30320f2743774cc89f12467ce5fd34724","tid":329394,"uid":36423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T14:19:07.000Z","msg":"Boss club?"},{"pid":"c605d6f209bf560ed1958d5b87266b77b8f64ca5","tid":329394,"uid":51348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T19:00:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/iusjw6lm\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fiusjw6lm&h=29781873&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女上黎開party<br />\n準備玩房game<br />\n大家有咩提議"},{"pid":"84a13991fa8eb246168999499762a4b5b08cf9c9","tid":329394,"uid":65612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T13:09:51.000Z","msg":"lm 高汁"},{"pid":"614661aa68fd0c1e9138b11c7c43d66d9634f2f5","tid":329394,"uid":83807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T13:14:43.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"fad8f1c2c66d47577d7eb7b9dcd51dd28957ba7c","tid":329394,"uid":25214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T13:15:08.000Z","msg":"咩價錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ff29a764f7be1d8399cffc899a40c530798eebd","tid":329394,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T13:17:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b41e44a1997712406227d96b85a009f993e02a57","tid":329394,"uid":51348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T0